Not a care in the world when you’re a lion cub! 🦁 

Throwback to special time spent with the Serian pride during my time in Mara North @alexwalkerserian ! 

TAKE ME BACK! ❤️ 🇰🇪 

#wildlife #wildlifephotography #nature #naturephotography #animal #animals #animalphotography #travel #travelgram #kenya #masaimara  #photography #wilderness #africa #african #safari #africansafari #bestnatureshot 
#lioncubs  #photography #animalsofinstagram
@kimsharps1 I love them! Thank you so much 😊
They are so cute a wonderful video 🥰
@watson_thedoguedebordeaux absolutely! Hopefully they all make it ❤️
Wow! So so so tiny 💚 future kings and queens of the Mara 🐾
@at_home_with_the_blacks aw thank you so much Rebecca!❤️
Omg this is utterly adorable Cathan!!! The world needs to see this♥️♥️♥️
Как милы эти очаровательные детки !!!Восторг и восхищения не имеют предела!!!,,🙏💙🔥🔥🔥
@batzellapaola ah thank you! I’ve been wanting to use this audio for so long now and just didn’t have the right clip 🙈 so glad it’s worked well!
@bush_maniac haha. Exactly! Me too! Mine was for a recently born tree kangaroo with mum. The sweetest thing ever! 😊 Amazing work as always! 🙌
Love it! I just did a similar reel with this track. It’s so perfect! 🥰🥰
@me.adventurer never EVER get tired of this 🥹
